# Paths copied (cp -RP, preserves symlinks) from the main worktree into
# each new worktree by `mise run worktree:add`. One path per line, relative
# to the repo root. Missing entries are skipped with a warning.
#
# Use for gitignored state the worktree needs but shouldn't share live with
# main (vaulted secrets, generated symlinks). For multi-GB shared artifacts
# like packer/artifacts, the task uses a real symlink instead — edit the
# task directly.
.ansible-mitogen-strategy
